D></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#EAEAEA>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#EAEAEA><font class="bfont"><B>Ken B</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#EAEAEA><font class="bfont">I noticed that awhile back--if you post a comment from within the editorial, you get the "old" Premium member post (non blue, with the tm symbol and the black premium sign in the left column). <br><BR><font size=1>11:10 10-11-2006</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>sithborg279</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont">All better now.  The world of Decktech is back in harmony. <br><BR><font size=1>11:09 10-11-2006</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#EAEAEA><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#EAEAEA><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/wars/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#EAEAEA><font class="bfont">huh, yeah, that is weird! This is slightly older code that was copied off the main buzzboard page and put on Tj&#39;s page and thus Ben&#39;s.<br />
